trans-unit.source: Configures an HTTP handler for a Web application.
trans-unit.target: Konfigurerer en HTTP-behandling for et webprogram.

trans-unit.source: The HttpHandlersSection class provides a way to programmatically access and modify the `httpHandlers` section of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Klassen HttpHandlersSection gjør det mulig å programmatisk tilgang til og endre den `httpHandlers` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: This type is part of a group that includes the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerAction> and the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerActionCollection> types.
trans-unit.target: Denne typen er en del av en gruppe som inneholder den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerAction>og <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerActionCollection>typer.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerActionCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerAction>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The HttpHandlersSection can read and write information from and to the related section of the configuration file according to the <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A> section property whose value is <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For HttpHandlersSection kan lese og skrive informasjon fra og relaterte delen av konfigurasjonsfilen i henhold til <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A>delen egenskapen der verdien er <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition>.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition> </xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlersSection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlersSection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The HttpHandlersSection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren HttpHandlersSection skal ikke brukes direkte fra koden.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
You obtain an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlersSection> class by using the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du hente en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlersSection>klassen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlersSection>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerActionCollection"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerAction"></xref> objects contained by the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlersSection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerActionCollection"> </xref> samling <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerAction"> </xref> objekter som inneholder den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlersSection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The Handlers property collection returned by this method does not refer to any actual element in the underlying configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Behandlingsprogrammer egenskapsutvalg som er returnert av denne metoden refererer ikke til noen faktiske element i underliggende konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: It is a <xref:System.Web.Configuration> construct that allows easy access to the handlers it contains.
trans-unit.target: Det er en <xref:System.Web.Configuration>konstruksjon som gir enkel tilgang til behandlingsprogrammer den inneholder.</xref:System.Web.Configuration>

trans-unit.source: This is a common pattern for handling the elements of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en vanlig mønster for håndtering av elementene i en konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerActionCollection"></xref> that contains the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerAction"></xref> objects, or handlers.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerActionCollection"> </xref> som inneholder den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpHandlerAction"> </xref> objekter eller behandlingsprogrammer.
